SPECIAL ACTIONS
q quit		(no! :-))
p, space	pause the game (take a break?)

MOVE
h, left arrow	move the worm left
j, down arrow	move the worm down
k, up arrow	move the worm up
l, right arrow	move the worm right

MODES
t		trick mode on/off
a		auto mode on/off

COMMAND LINE OPTIONS
-a start the game with auto mode set to on
